longBusinessSummary: Sibek AB (publ) engages in the investigation, planning, project designing and safety reviewing, inspection, and commissioning management of railway signaling systems in Sweden. It also offers connection management, construction site follow-up, construction inspection, and construction management services. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Årsta, Sweden.
